20content%20partnership%20with%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMitchell%20Smith%2C%20X's%20head%20of%20original%20content%2C%20says%20the%20company's%20video%20ventures%20this%20year%20have%20moved%20from%20the%20%26quot%3Bcrawl%26quot%3B%20stage%20to%20%26quot%3Bwalk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20world-class%20athletes%20and%20creators%20in%20their%20own%20right%20like%20Serena%20and%20Venus%20willing%20to%20launch%20a%20show%20with%20us%20is%20a%20great%20illustration%20of%20the%20evolution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fserena-williams-net-worth-and-career-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWilliams%20sisters%3C%2Fa%3E'%20decision%20to%20launch%20a%20new%20video%20podcast%20on%20X%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20recently%20launched%20%26quot%3BNFL%20Top%20100%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20100-episode%20original%20that's%20an%20adaptation%20of%20the%20league's%20special%20featuring%20the%20top%20players%20as%20voted%20by%20their%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20X%20has%20released%20more%20than%20300%20episodes%20of%20content%20across%2018%20originals%20since%20launching%20the%20effort%20in%20early%202024%2C%20which%20it%20says%20has%20yielded%20more%20than%20700%20million%20video%20views%20and%202%20billion%20impressions.%20Smith%20said%20X%20wants%20to%20double%20that%20output%20over%20the%20next%20year%20and%20a%20half.%20That%20would%20still%20be%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20competitors%20like%20YouTube%2C%20which%20gets%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thewrap.com%2Fyoutube-shorts-200-billion-daily-views%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehundreds%20of%20billions%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20video%20views%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20X%20has%20a%20bespoke%20catalog%20of%20shows%2C%20its%20pitch%20to%20creators%20is%20closer%20to%20YouTube%20than%20streamers%20like%20Netflix.%20X%20is%20not%20throwing%20any%20development%20money%20to%20shows%20branded%20as%20originals%20or%20buying%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20it's%20pitching%20creators%20on%20monetizing%20their%20videos%20through%20X%20Amplify%2C%20its%20video%20ad%20sales%20tool%2C%20and%20offering%20to%20build%20custom%20ad%20treatments%20for%20shows.%20The%20creator%20gets%20a%20certain%20percentage%20of%20the%20ad%20revenue%20based%20on%20specific%20contract%20negotiations.%20Unlike%20YouTube%2C%20X%20doesn't%20have%20a%20standard%20rate.%20X%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20split.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222454%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Serena%20Williams%20is%20congratulated%20by%20her%20sister%20and%20opponent%20Venus%20Williams%20following%20their%20ladies'%20singles%20third-round%20match%20on%20Day%20Five%20of%20the%202018%20US%20Open.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65650f14fe5bc6545ebcaf69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221908%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVenus%20Williams%20(left)%20and%20Serena%20Williams%20are%20launching%20a%20show%20on%20X.%3Cp%3EJulian%20Finney%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f19b7a29-f9f9-4ff3-a496-7132b6cc3105%5C%22%3EX%20is%20pitching%20culture%2C%20not%20politics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20said%20one%20of%20X's%20selling%20points%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20build%20series%20around%20newsmaking%20moments.%20It's%20starting%20to%20build%20shows%20tied%20to%20creators%20around%20big%20events%20like%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20inherently%20social%20platform%20that%20now%20has%20a%20great%20video%20viewing%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20because%20it's%20the%20first%20place%20people%20check%2C%20it's%20really%20the%20one%20platform%20that%20truly%20moves%20at%20the%20velocity%20of%20culture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20X%2C%20video%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20boost%20user%20engagement%20while%20moving%20the%20platform%20toward%20sports%20and%20lifestyle%20content%20and%20away%20from%20hot-button%20political%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20looking%20to%20work%20with%20strong%20creators%2C%20whether%20that's%20endemic%20creators%2C%20athletes%2C%20musicians%2C%20actors%2C%20or%20even%20sports%20teams%20in%20leagues%2C%20in%20the%20most%20highly%20engaged%20content%20categories%20on%20the%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp%20next%2C%20Smith%20said%20he's%20pursuing%20more%20projects%20with%20the%20NFL.%20He's%20also%20looking%20for%20more%20finance-focused%20shows%20in%20the%20vein%20of%20Anthony%20Pompliano's%20daily%20business%20show%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20Desk%20of%20Anthony%20Pompliano%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20female-aimed%20fare%20like%20Khlo%C3%A9%20Kardashian's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fi%2Fevents%2F1875987636159905792%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKhlo%C3%A9%20in%20Wonderland%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20podcast%20and%20Alexis%20Ohanian-produced%20%26quot%3BThe%20Offseason%26quot%3B%20about%20women's%20soccer.%20(Ohanian%20is%20married%20to%20Serena%20Williams).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20categories%2C%20Smith%20has%20ambitions%20for%20series%20that%20take%20viewers%20behind%20the%20scenes%20with%20music%20artists%20and%20gamers%2C%20and%20competition%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20love%20to%20crack%20a%20daily%20game%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223db785fc-4636-4984-ac8c-71162dc3a6ca%5C%22%3EX%20faces%20some%20skepticism%20about%20its%20video%20plans%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EX%20still%20needs%20to%20convince%20more%20producers%20and%20advertisers%20that%20it's%20a%20worthwhile%20destination%20for%20their%20time%20and%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Smith's%20former%20boss%2C%20Brett%20Weitz%2C%20left%20in%20April%20after%20about%20two%20years%20as%20X's%20global%20head%20of%20content%2C%20talent%2C%20and%20brand%20sales%20and%20wasn't%20replaced%2C%2