the%2070s%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20BC.%20When%20people%20ask%20us%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-of-strong-marriage-couples-therapist-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecret%20to%20a%20long%20marriage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Barry%20and%20I%20chuckle%20ruefully%20and%20reply%20half-jokingly%2C%20%26quot%3BSkip%20the%20first%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20true%20%E2%80%94%20the%20initial%20chapter%20in%20our%20marriage%20was%20rough%2C%20but%20we%20did%20ultimately%20succeed%2C%20and%20we%20attribute%20our%20success%20partly%20to%20the%20three%20ground%20rules%20we%20developed%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239b884aa-48c0-4d4a-afef-6afe128edd99%5C%22%3EHaving%20a%20lot%20of%20space%20is%20important%20to%20us%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20motto%20is%20%26quot%3Bintimacy%20and%20independence.%26quot%3B%20We%20enjoy%20spending%20time%20both%20together%20and%20apart%2C%20so%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhusband-wife-spend-time-apart-marriage-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egive%20each%20other%20a%20lot%20of%20freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20spending%20about%20four%20weeks%20a%20year%20on%20our%20own.%20We%20have%20an%20ideal%20opportunity%20to%20practice%20this%2C%20as%20we%20live%20part%20of%20the%20year%20in%20Guanajuato%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20part%20of%20the%20year%20in%20California.%20In%20the%20fall%2C%20I%20fly%20from%20our%20home%20in%20California%20to%20Guanajuato%20about%20two%20weeks%20before%20Barry%2C%20and%20in%20the%20spring%2C%20he%20returns%20to%20California%20two%20weeks%20earlier%20than%20I%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20disruption%20in%20our%20marriage%20routine%20feels%20liberating%2C%20since%20all%20our%20usual%20patterns%20loosen%20up%20%E2%80%94%20sleeping%2C%20eating%2C%20and%20socializing%20differently.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20Guanajuato%2C%20I%20join%20a%20Sunday%20women's%20hiking%20group%2C%20which%20I%20rarely%20do%20when%20Barry's%20in%20town%20because%20on%20Sundays%20we%20go%20cycling.%20Of%20course%2C%20we%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarried-couple-doesnt-live-together-anymore-it-improved-relationship-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egive%20each%20other%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20we're%20together%2C%20but%20the%20period%20of%20two%20weeks%20apart%20twice%20a%20year%20gives%20us%20even%20more%20time%20to%20replenish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e704c27-29f7-418e-8aab-790e3fff0f8c%5C%22%3EWe%20don't%20play%20tit-for-tat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20say%20I%20wash%20the%20dishes%20after%20dinner%20one%20evening.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20I%20don't%20get%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20washed%20them%20last%20night%2C%20so%20it's%20your%20turn.%26quot%3B%20In%20other%20words%2C%20we%20can't%20use%20a%20choice%20we%20made%20as%20a%20bargaining%20chip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floading-dishwasher-right-way-doing-it-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewash%20the%20dishes%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20not%20wash%20the%20dishes%2C%20but%20if%20we%20choose%20to%20do%20them%2C%20the%20action%20stands%20alone%2C%20free%20of%20expectations%20or%20obligations.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20either%20do%20things%20freely%20or%20not%20at%20all.%20It's%20not%20a%20perfect%20system%2C%20of%20course%2C%20but%20rarely%20does%20either%20of%20us%20feel%20like%20a%20martyr.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScore-keeping%20was%20a%20huge%20source%20of%20contention%20with%20his%20first%20wife%2C%20and%20it%20was%20clear%20early%20on%20that%20Barry%20wanted%20to%20change%20that%20pattern.%20I%20agree%20that%20it's%20been%20good%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22633%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20smiling%20with%20a%20mountain%20view%20behind%20them.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686bfb1e85e81483682d7a21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20have%20created%20a%20set%20of%20rules%20for%20their%20relationship%20that%20they%20credit%20their%20success%20to.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Louisa%20Rogers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229083c39f-e036-4709-be69-d40feea6a483%5C%22%3EWe%20don't%20bring%20up%20painful%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERevisiting%20difficult%20issues%20was%20once%20our%20toughest%20issue.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20sometimes%20one%20or%20the%20other%20of%20us%20(OK%2C%20usually%20me!)%20would%20bring%20up%20an%20old%20hurt%2C%20and%20we%20would%20delve%20back%20into%20our%20history%20and%20try%20to%20hash%20things%20out.%20Rarely%20did%20this%20work.%20Frequently%20we%20wouldn't%20even%20agree%20on%20what%20had%20happened%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboundaries-work-resentment-audit-productivity-executive-coach-melody-wilding-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresentments%20would%20inevitably%20resurface%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20we'd%20be%20%26quot%3Bprocessing%26quot%3B%20(a%20word%20Barry%20now%20abhors)%2C%20and%20he'd%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BDoes%20everything%20always%20have%20to%20be%20a%20workshop%20around%20here%3F%26quot%3B%20(I'd%20remind%20him%2C%20though%2C%20that%20we%20did%20meet%20in%20a%20workshop%2C%20after%20all!)%20So%2C%20as%20a%20sort%20of%20compromise%2C%20we've%20developed%20what%20we%20call%20our%20%26quot%3Bstatute%20of%20limitations%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20a%20point%20when%20we%20agree%20to%20no%20longer%20bring%20up%20a%20past%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20that%20we%20don't%20try%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-marriage-lessons-conflict-healthy-space-good-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresolve%20conflicts%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20one%20of%20us%20does%20something%20that%20bothers%20the%20other.%20But%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20conversations%2C%20assuming%20we've%20reached%20a%20resolution%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it's%20not%20perfect%20%E2%80%94%20then%20the%20subject%20is%20closed.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20it's%20no%20longer%20%26quot%3Bour%26quot%3B%20problem%3B%20it's%20his%20problem%20or%20mine%2C%20to%20handle%20independently%3A%20discuss%20it%20with%20a%20friend%2C%20write%20about%20it%2C%20or%20otherwise%20sort%20it%20out%20on%20our%20own%20without%20involving%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220af7fe27-94ee-4395-8f9b-f7f99e7eb1dd%5C%22%3EOur%20system%20works%20for%20us%2C%20even%20if%20we%20do%20screw%20up%20occasionally%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20we%20sometimes%20screw%20up.%20One%20of%20us%20occasionally%20does%20play%20tit-for-tat%2C%20or%20brings%20up%20something%20that%20we%20have%20closed%20the%20book%20on.%20If%20we%20do%2C%20the%20other%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20remember%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20agreements%20didn't%20arrive%20preserved%2C%20polished%2C%20and%20ready-made.%20Hardly!%20They%20evolved%20gradually%2C%20over%20years%20and%20years%20of%20practice%2C%20disagreements%2C%20difficult%20conversations%2C%20therapy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpsychedelics-key-long-happy-marriage-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epsychedelics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20what%20we%20call%20%26quot%3Bour%20dome%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20the%20safe%20place%20where%20we%20share%20with%20deep%20honesty%20something%20that%20is%20troubling%20us%20about%20the%20other.%20Hammering%20out%20our%20ground%20rules%20along%20the%20winding%20road%20of%20our%20marriage%20is%20part%20of%20what%20made%20us%20resilient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20have%20given%20us%20a%20deep%20foundation%20of%20trust.%20Without%20them%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20feel%20safe%20with%20each%20other%2C%20enjoy%20our%20lives%20as%20fully%2C%20or%20have%20so%20much%20fun%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuite%20simply%2C%20without%20these%20ground%20rul