its%20the%20spot.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Restaurant%20Association%20reported%20in%20April%20that%20nearly%2075%25%20of%20all%20restaurant%20traffic%20now%20happens%20off-premises%20in%20takeout%2C%20drive-thru%2C%20and%20delivery%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20McDonald's%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20how%20first-day%20sales%20have%20gone%2C%20how%20many%20restaurants%20participated%20in%20the%20promotion%2C%20or%20how%20long%20customers%20can%20expect%20to%20see%20the%20spicy%20pepper%20sauce%20as%20an%20option%20for%20their%20morning%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-worker-age-84-retired-45-years-fast-food-employment-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%20employee%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20location%20I%20visited%2C%20who%20was%20not%20authorized%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20record%2C%20said%20the%20spicy%20McMuffin%20items%20had%20been%20extremely%20popular%20the%20morning%20of%20their%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20employee%20couldn't%20specify%20how%20many%20had%20been%20sold%20by%20the%20time%20breakfast%20hours%20ended%20at%2010%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20they%20said%20there%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Btons%26quot%3B%20of%20orders%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20I%20left%20thinking%20I'd%20happily%20eat%20a%20spicy%20McMuffin%20again%2C%20though%20the%20old%20classic%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20humble%20hash%20brown%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0remains%20the%20top%20dog%20on%20the%20McDonald's%20breakfast%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-new-menu-spicy-egg-mcmuffin-breakfast-taste-test-hashbrowns-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752052922000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d792185e81483682d97ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22ori