ent%20is%20like%20stepping%20into%20the%20pit%20of%20a%20rock%20concert.%20It's%20loud%2C%20it's%20electric%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20little%20chaotic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20of%20it%20like%20a%20family%20reunion%2C%20where%20you're%20actually%20excited%20to%20see%20everybody%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20COO%20of%20the%20community%2C%20Eugene%20Khayman%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20high-energy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMillion%20Dollar%20Sellers%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mds.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMDS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20consists%20of%20Amazon%20sellers%20and%20e-commerce%20entrepreneurs%20who%20bring%20in%20at%20least%20%241%20million%20in%20annual%20revenue.%20Events%20%E2%80%94%20in%20which%20community%20members%20connect%20in%20person%2C%20trade%20ideas%2C%20and%20swap%20strategies%20%E2%80%94%20are%20just%20one%20aspect%20of%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20center%20of%20it%20is%20still%20a%20Facebook%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Khayman.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20your%20collective%2024%2F7%20brain%20trust%20so%2C%20at%20any%20point%20in%20time%2C%20you%20can%20drop%20a%20question.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20came%20across%20the%20group%20in%202016%2C%20a%20few%20years%20after%20he%20started%20selling%20kitchen%20products%20on%20Amazon.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20it%20was%20a%20Facebook%20group%20for%20private%20label%20sellers%20doing%20at%20least%20%2410%2C000%20in%20monthly%20revenue.%20The%20threshold%20grew%20to%20%2450%2C000%20a%20month%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20%241%20million%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhayman%20said%20that%20joining%20the%20group%20made%20business%20more%20fun%20while%20helping%20him%20stay%20competitive.%20His%20brand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fepare.com%2Fpages%2Fabout%3Fsrsltid%3DAfmBOooM6JXqZdu2tWiHvriJnYGtKtLEQw2MJW7HTkJZTNSEw0wYbeVw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eepar%C3%A9%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20hit%20the%20seven-figure%20annual%20revenue%20mark%2C%20but%20sales%20started%20dropping%20as%20e-comm%20grew%20in%20popularity%20and%20new%20sellers%20burst%20onto%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20strategies%20that%20people%20were%20using%20that%20were%20destroying%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20keeping%20up%20with%20the%20information%20fast%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20his%20idea%20to%20bring%20the%20MDS%20Facebook%20group%20to%20life%20through%20in-person%20events.%20He%20organized%20the%20first%20one%20at%20an%20all-inclusive%20resort%20in%20Canc%C3%BAn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20charged%20people%20%2499%20for%20a%20ticket%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20lost%20money%20on%20it%20because%20I%20thought%20all-inclusive%20meant%20that%20you%20didn't%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Khayman%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20bill%20was%20worth%20it.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20amazing%20energy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20live%20events%20took%20off%2C%20so%20did%20the%20community.%20As%20of%202025%2C%20there%20are%20about%20700%20MDS%20members%20who%20pay%20%247%2C497%20a%20year%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhayman%20still%20runs%20two%20e-comm%20brands%2C%20but%20said%20he%20prefers%20to%20direct%20more%20of%20his%20time%20and%20energy%20to%20growing%20MDS%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20I%20did%20all%20of%20these%20events%2C%20I%20saw%20people%20coming%20together%20and%20I%20saw%20how%20much%20was%20being%20created%20from%20those%20relationships.%20I%20was%20getting%20a%20lot%20more%20fulfillment%20from%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a22b8972-f707-46df-aac6-3abf971effd9%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20get%20into%20the%20MDS%20club%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20process%20has%20evolved%20as%20the%20MDS%20community%20has%20grown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20very%2C%20very%20beginning%2C%20it%20was%20quite%20simple%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Khayman.%20Prospective%20members%20would%20email%20the%20MDS%20founder%20a%20copy%20of%20their%20photo%20ID%20and%20a%20screenshot%20of%20their%20sales.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20group%20gained%20more%20exposure%20and%20applications%20started%20flowing%20in%2C%20the%20process%20became%20more%20rigorous%2C%20primarily%20so%20that%20MDS%20could%20maintain%20its%20core%20identity.%20%26quot%3BNo%20community%20ever%20wants%20to%20get%20bigger.%20That's%20always%20a%20thing%2C%20like%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20lose%20its%20charm%20if%20it%20gets%20too%20big.%20And%20everybody%20wanted%20to%20really%20preserve%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDHzOQRJSwcm%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDHzOQRJSwcm%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDHzOQRJSwcm%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Million%20Dollar%20Sellers%20(%40mdsonly)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20interview%20is%20meant%20to%20screen%20for%20a%20type%20of%20person%2C%20not%20necessarily%20a%20type%20of%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20need%20to%20have%20the%20mindset%20that%20they're%20coming%20in%20here%20to%20help%20and%20share%20and%20become%20a%20member%20of%20the%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Khayman.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20people%20come%20in%20with%20some%20kind%20of%20agenda%20to%20sell%20some%20other%20product%20or%20service%2C%20so%20it's%20meant%20to%20filter%20for%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20group's%20core%20values%20is%3A%20Give%20more%2C%20get%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20big%20thing%20we%20try%20to%20instill%20in%20everybody%2C%20so%20there's%20not%20really%20much%20judgment%20or%20flash%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Khayman.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20people%20that%20are%20really%20deep%20in%20their%20businesses%20and%20just%20wanting%20to%20help%20one%20another.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20interview%20is%20complete%20and%20the%20application%20is%20approved%2C%20members%20gain%20access%20to%20exclusive%20events%2C%20a%20network%20of%20high-level%20sellers%2C%20and%20online%20groups%20that%20share%20insights%2C%20experiences%2C%20and%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%20of%20growing%2C%20Khayman%20recognizes%20the%20immense%20benefits%20of%20having%20more%20members.%20It%20allows%20specific%20sub-groups%20to%20form%2C%20so%20sellers%20in%20the%20kitchen%20space%20or%20supplement%20space%2C%20for%20example%2C%20can%20discuss%20their%20industry-specific%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20enough%20members%20in%20each%20of%20these%20specific%20domains%20to%20give%20each%20other%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8cb35cf-723f-41cc-85a9-ec68a1e494cf%5C%22%3EThe%20future%20of%20MDS%3A%20Thinking%20beyond%20Amazon%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESelling%20on%20Amazon%20has%20never%20been%20more%20complex%20and%20competitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Khayman%20started%20in%20the%20early%202010s%2C%20%26quot%3Bmy%20first%20year%20of%20selling%20on%20Amazon%2C%20I%20sold%20%24150%2C000%20worth%20of%20pepper%20grinders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20were%20pepper%20grinders%20that%20I%20was%20buying%20for%20%245%20and%20selling%20for%20%2450%20on%20Amazon.%20I%20took%20home%2080%25%20of%20that%20as%20profit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20it's%20much%20harder%20to%20run%20a%20profitable%20Amazon%20business.%20The%20fees%20are%20higher%2C%20the%20competition%20is%20stiffer%2C%20and%20the%20strategies%20are%20constantly%20evolving.%20Tariffs%20added%20an%20entirely%20new%20level%20of%20complexity%20at%20the%20start%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20long%20time%2C%20we%20were%20a%20very%20Amazon-focused%20community%2C%20and%20we've%20been%20trying%20to%20break%20away%20from%20that%20overall%20stigma%20and%20just%20be%20a%20general%20community%20for%20e-commerce%20founders%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Khayman.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20nice%20to%20see%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20that%20people%20coming%20into%20the%20group%20have%20a%20wider%20understanding%20of%20e-commerce.%20Amazon%20is%20just%20a%20part%20of%20their%20business%2C%20rather%20than%20their%20whole%20business%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that%20aligns%20with%20the%20future.%20If%20people%20are%20treating%20Amazon%20as%20their%20whole%20business%2C%20they're%20definitely%20more%20at%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20big%20selling%20opportunity%20right%20now%20on%20TikTok%2C%20for%20example.%20He%20said%20the%20current%20TikTok%20marketplace%20reminds%20him%20of%20Amazon%20in%20the%20early%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20member%20of%20a%20group%20like%20MDS%20helps%20entrepreneurs%20spot%20these%20trends%2C%20adapt%2C%20and%20stay%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20can%2