%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump's%20immigration%20crackdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20forcing%20investors%20to%20examine%20the%20employee%20base%20of%20US%20companies%20they%20may%20be%20looking%20to%20acquire%20more%20closely%2C%20said%20Ted%20Chiappari%2C%20partner%20and%20head%20of%20immigration%20at%20the%20law%20firm%20Duane%20Morris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20working%20on%20one%20merger%20acquisition%20now%2C%20and%20that's%20their%20phase%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chiappari.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20check%20out%20the%20staffing%20first%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20their%20I-9s%20are%20in%20order%20before%20they%20go%20forward%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20deal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20law%20requires%20that%20anyone%20hired%20to%20work%20in%20the%20US%20fill%20out%20a%20I-9%20to%20verify%20their%20identity%20and%20employment%20authorization.%20Chiappari%20said%20it's%20long%20been%20a%20required%20piece%20of%20M%26amp%3BA%20due%20diligence%20but%20that%20many%20investors%20treat%20it%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bafterthought.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20even%20considered%20it%20at%20all%2C%20they%20would%20just%20sort%20of%20shrug%20their%20shoulders%20and%20say%2C%20'Look%2C%20if%20we%20get%20hit%20with%20a%20I-9%20audit%2C%20we'll%20pay%20whatever%20penalties%20there%20are%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Trump's%20policies%20are%20prompting%20firms%20to%20move%20the%201-9%20due%20diligence%20component%20up%20the%20priority%20list.%20Failure%20to%20do%20so%20could%20mean%20getting%20stuck%20running%20a%20company%20without%20enough%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20concerned%20because%20that%20really%20affects%20the%20viability%20of%20the%20business%20if%20they%20end%20up%20losing%2025%25%20of%20their%20workforce%20or%20end%20up%20having%20to%20pay%20a%20lot%20more%20money%20to%20find%20replacements%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20a%20suit%20named%20Ted%20Chiappari%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d4fda85e81483682d9276%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETed%20Chiappari%20of%20law%20firm%20Duane%20Morris%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Duane%20Morris%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1fd313f-c0e9-4088-bdea-673c88012586%5C%22%3ETravel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIsha%20Atassi%2C%20a%20partner%20with%20the%20law%20firm%20Fragomen%20in%20New%20York%2C%20said%20her%20financial%20clients%20are%20largely%20taking%20a%20%26quot%3Bbusiness%20as%20usual%26quot%3B%20approach%20to%20travel%20%E2%80%94%20even%20as%20other%20sectors%20take%20a%20more%20aggressive%20stance%2C%20issuing%20advisories%20or%20tightening%20guidance%20around%20international%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnxieties%20over%20travel%20are%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Dowding%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20RBC's%20BlueBay%20unit%2C%20said%20neither%20he%20nor%20his%20team%20has%20slowed%20their%20travel.%20However%2C%20the%20British%20citizen%20is%20more%20worried%20than%20before%20about%20being%20turned%20away%20at%20the%20border%2C%20in%20part%20because%20he%20writes%20a%20weekly%20note%20that%20has%20occasionally%20been%20critical%20of%20Trump's%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20I'm%20taking%20a%20personal%20risk%2C%20but%20I'm%20putting%20myself%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20say%20I%20can't%20come%20in%2C%20then%20I%20can't%20come%20in.%20So%20be%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConcerns%20over%20border%20crossing%20are%20also%20leading%20to%20more%20conversations%20about%20travel%20visas%20and%20how%20to%20talk%20to%20border%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20a%20lot%20more%20efforts%20to%20educate%20as%20to%20what%20should%20be%20said%20or%20what%20can%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chiappari.%20He%20pointed%2C%20as%20an%20example%2C%20to%20a%20professional%20coming%20to%20the%20US%20for%20a%20business%20meeting%20or%20conference.%20While%20it's%20technically%20work%2C%20it's%20not%20%26quot%3Bproducing%20something%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20which%20might%20mean%20avoiding%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bwork%26quot%3B%20when%20talking%20to%20border%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20generally%20avoid%20the%20W%20word%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20border%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a%20hijab%20named%20Isha%20Atassi%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d5054f748d8c055f52bb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIsha%20Atassi%2C%20a%20partner%20with%20the%20law%20firm%20Fragomen%20in%20New%20York%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Fragomen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb106a83-23f4-4e0f-a7b6-60514d466cd9%5C%22%3EHiring%20and%20staffing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20outside%20the%20US%20are%20viewing%20the%20US%20crackdown%20as%20a%20potential%20poaching%20opportunity.%20For%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fasia-multi-strat-hedge-funds-booming-tapping-middle-east-talent-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDanny%20Yong%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20Dymon%20Asia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Singapore-based%20hedge%20fund%20with%20offices%20across%20Asia%2C%20said%20his%20firm%20is%20targeting%20immigrant%20portfolio%20managers%20based%20in%20the%20US%20who%20might%20be%20interested%20in%20returning%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImmigration%20lawyers%20said%20they're%20seeing%20little%20to%20no%20slowdown%20in%20the%20financial%20industry's%20appetite%20for%20foreign%20labor%2C%20however%2C%20although%20the%20process%20is%20taking%20longer%20than%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20an%20understanding%20that%20the%20process%20may%20take%20longer%20and%20may%20be%20met%20with%20more%20challenges%20by%20way%20of%20requests%20for%20evidence%20or%20denials%2C%20and%20we%20are%20helping%20to%20manage%20timing%20expectations%20and%20flagging%20high-risk%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Atassi%20of%20the%20Fragomen%20law%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20is%20that%20financial%20firms%20tend%20to%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20overseas%20offices%2C%20so%20if%20a%20firm%20hires%20someone%20who%20doesn't%20get%20the%20right%20US%20visa%2C%20they%20can%20just%20park%20them%20in%20a%20non-US%20office%20for%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20money%2C%20and%20so%20if%20they've%20got%20a%20superstar%20on%20their%20team%2C%20transferring%20someone%20to%20the%20London%20office%20for%20a%20year%20or%20two%20is%20just%20not%20going%20to%20make%20or%20break%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chiappari.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20rounding%20error%20for%20these%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20stars%20also%20have%20more%20visa%20options%20than%2C%20say%2C%20the%20average%20data%20scientist%2C%20Chiappari%20said.%20He%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-visa-moved-usa-canada-immigrants-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EO-1%20visa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20reserved%20for%20people%20who%20have%20reached%20national%20or%20international%20acclaim%20and%20sit%20at%20the%20top%20of%20their%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20a%20lot%20easier%20for%20a%20Morgan%20Stanley%20or%20a%20JPMorgan%20to%20say%2C%20'This%20person's%20exceptional%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20are%20responsible%20for%20%26quot%3Bfrontpage%20deals%20that%20everyone's%20heard%20about.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-immigration-crackdown-wall-street-mergers-border-crossings-hiring-staffing-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%