trillion%20in%20federal%20spending%20reductions%20to%20Medicaid%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%20Alongside%20new%20requirements%20that%20non-exempt%20recipients%20work%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirees-unretiring-returning-to-work-worry-snap-medicaid-disability-benefits-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E80%20hours%20a%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20order%20to%20qualify%20for%20insurance%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Beautiful%20Bill%26quot%3B%20restricts%20how%20much%20money%20states%20can%20funnel%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fcrs-product%2FRS22843%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovider%20taxes%3C%2Fa%3E%20toward%20Medicaid%20and%20limits%20some%20federal%20hospital%20spending%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aha.org%2Fnews%2Fheadline%2F2025-06-16-analysis-highlights-impact-proposed-medicaid-cuts-rural-patients-and-hospitals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eespecially%20in%20rural%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20practice%2C%20this%20could%20mean%20hospitals%20lose%20funding%2C%20and%20some%20Medicaid%20recipients%20could%20experience%20higher%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2Fsections%2Fshots-health-news%2F2025%2F07%2F02%2Fnx-s1-5453870%2Fsenate-republicans-tax-bill-medicaid-health-care%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eout-of-pocket%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%2C%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20Kush%20Desai%20said%20the%20president%20has%20made%20a%20%26quot%3Bclear%20pledge%26quot%3B%20while%20in%20office%2C%20vowing%20not%20to%20cut%20Medicaid%2C%20Medicare%2C%20or%20Social%20Security.%20Desai%20said%20Trump's%20spending%20plan%20%26quot%3Bonly%20addresses%20waste%2C%20fraud%2C%20and%20abuse%20to%20protect%20and%20preserve%20Medicaid%20for%20the%20Americans%20who%20rely%20on%20the%20program%20by%20implementing%20commonsense%20reforms%20like%20popular%20work%20requirements%20and%20income%20eligibility%20verification.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20analysis%20from%20health%20research%20and%20news%20platform%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kff.org%2Fmedicaid%2Fissue-brief%2Fallocating-cbos-estimates-of-federal-medicaid-spending-reductions-across-the-states-senate-reconciliation-bill%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKFF%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20Congressional%20Budget%20Office%20estimates%20found%20the%20reduction%20in%20federal%20spending%20for%20Medicaid%20over%202025%20to%202034%20could%20range%20from%206%25%20in%20Alabama%20and%20Wyoming%20to%2021%25%20in%20Louisiana%20and%20Virginia.%20Most%20states%20could%20have%20percent%20drops%20in%20the%20double%20digits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20analysis%20doesn't%20include%20how%20many%20people%20could%20be%20affected%20by%20these%20spending%20changes%2C%20government%20data%20shows%20about%201.4%20million%20people%20in%20Louisiana%20and%20about%201.6%20million%20in%20Virginia%20were%20enrolled%20in%20Medicaid%20this%20March.%20Reductions%20in%20federal%20healthcare%20spending%20could%20impact%20those%20not%20enrolled%20in%20Medicaid%20by%20disrupting%20funding%20that%20some%20local%20hospitals%20need%20to%20stay%20operational%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kff.org%2Fpolicy-watch%2Fhow-might-federal-medicaid-cuts-in-the-senate-passed-reconciliation-bill-affect-rural-areas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKFF%20also%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20hover%20over%20the%20map%20to%20see%20the%20estimates%20of%20spending%20reductions%20in%20each%20state%2C%20per%20KFF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FaijQ7%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Medicaid%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22395%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EKFF's%20analysis%20had%20some%20limitations.%20KFF%20said%20CBO's%20estimates%20were%20based%20on%20an%20earlier%20version%20of%20the%20bill%3B%20changes%20were%20made%20in%20the%20final%20version%20that%20passed%20Congress%20late%20last%20week.%20KFF%20used%20previous%20estimates%20and%20made%20adjustments%20based%20on%20some%20changes%20made.%20KFF%20also%20didn't%20examine%20the%20effects%20of%20a%20%2450%20billion%20program%20funding%20grants%20to%20states%20for%20rural%20healthcare%20added%20to%20the%20bill%20%26quot%3Band%20did%20not%20account%20for%20other%20changes%20to%20the%20legislative%20language%20that%20were%20more%20complicated%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bapplying%20new%20restrictions%20on%20provider%20taxes%20to%20local%20government%20taxes%20in%20expansion%20states.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208074483-8dfd-4bc7-aa48-0103ba6663ff%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Trump's%20spending%20bill%20means%20for%20children%2C%20low-income%20Americans%2C%20states%2C%20and%20rural%20hospitals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20March%2C%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medicaid.gov%2Fmedicaid%2Fprogram-information%2Fmedicaid-and-chip-enrollment-data%2Freport-highlights%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E79%20million%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20received%20coverage%20under%20Medicaid%20or%20the%20Children's%20Health%20Insurance%20Program.%20The%20insurance%20can%20cover%20doctor%20appointments%2C%20hospital%20visits%2C%20long-term%20care%2C%20prescription%20drugs%2C%20and%20lab%20testing.%20Eligibility%20varies%20across%20the%20country%3B%20recipients%20need%20to%20have%20an%20income%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoverty-line-leaves-behind-low-income-americans-snap-medicare-wic-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enear%20the%20poverty%20line%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20qualify%20in%20most%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-gop-proposes-medicaid-cuts-would-impact-kids-lower-earners-2025-5%5C%22%20targe