0regulator%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BNetting%26quot%3B%20is%20another%20offbeat%20way%20Russia%20is%20using%20to%20beat%20sweeping%20sanctions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERussia's%20economy%20faces%20challenges%2C%20with%20a%20potential%20recession%20and%20slowing%20GDP%20growth.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Frussia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussia's%3C%2Fa%3E%20top%20financial%20watchdog%20has%20offered%20a%20rare%20glimpse%20into%20how%20the%20country's%20businesses%20are%20sidestepping%20sweeping%20Western%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYury%20Chikhanchin%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Russia's%20Federal%20Service%20for%20Financial%20Monitoring%2C%20told%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20companies%20are%20turning%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fgold%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egold%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20and%20creative%20accounting%20tricks%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Kremlin%20transcript.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20approaches%20add%20to%20other%20unconventional%20tactics%20%E2%80%94%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-barter-pakistan-mounting-sanctions-western-war-allies-international-trade-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebarter%20trade%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20that%20Russia%20is%20using%20to%20skirt%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlternative%20payment%20mechanisms%20are%20being%20actively%20employed%2C%20including%20gold%2C%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20and%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20netting%20arrangements%3A%20clearing%20operations%2C%20which%20we%20are%20currently%20implementing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chikhanchin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChikhanchin's%20mention%20of%20%26quot%3Bnetting%20arrangements%26quot%3B%20refers%20to%20a%20workaround%20in%20which%20exporters%20and%20importers%20offset%20what%20they%20owe%20each%20other.%20Banks%20balance%20the%20export%20and%20import%20payments%20of%20different%20companies%20at%20a%20central%20location.%20This%20process%20minimizes%20the%20need%20to%20move%20money%20across%20borders%2C%20avoiding%20a%20key%20chokepoint%20for%20international%20sanctions%20enforcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2227c20ecc-ca7a-4032-a24d-519845cb58cd%5C%22%3ERussia's%20shifting%20focus%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChikhanchin's%20unusually%20public%20disclosure%20of%20how%20Russia%20is%20circumventing%20sanctions%20comes%20over%2040%20months%20after%20Moscow's%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20triggered%20an%20unprecedented%20wave%20of%20Western%20sanctions.%20Despite%2017%20rounds%20of%20penalties%20from%20the%20European%20Union%20%E2%80%94%20once%20Russia's%20largest%20trading%20partner%20%E2%80%94%20the%20country's%20economy%20continues%20to%20hum%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChikhanchin%20said%20Russia's%20cross-border%20payments%20are%20now%20flowing%20more%20through%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20and%20Central%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20shift%20aligns%20with%20the%20development%20of%20a%20unified%20fast%20payment%20system%20that%20serves%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20SWIFT%2C%20primarily%20involving%20CIS%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Commonwealth%20of%20Independent%20States%2C%20a%20group%20of%20former%20Soviet%20republics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20meeting%2C%20Chikhanchin%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20share%20of%20the%20ruble%2C%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20and%20gold%20in%20trade%20settlements%20has%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20share%20of%20payments%20in%20dollars%2C%20euros%2C%20and%20pounds%20has%20%26quot%3Bdropped%20significantly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22244b493e-c1e4-4757-9277-6c6e4e14bdc1%5C%22%3ESanctions%20are%20starting%20to%20bite%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Russia's%20economy%20has%20appeared%20to%20be%20resi