to%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Chopra%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CChange%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20start%20with%20something%20big.%20It%20begins%20with%20one%20step.%20One%20skill.%20One%20woman%20finding%20her%20voice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20encourages%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20contribute%2C%20whether%20with%20fabric%2C%20time%2C%20or%20funds%2C%20to%20reach%20out.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20a%20skill%2C%20teach%20it.%20If%20you%20can%20donate%20something%2C%20do%20it.%20It%20all%20goes%20into%20building%20someone%E2%80%99s%20confidence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20that%20often%20tells%20women%20to%20stay%20small%2C%20this%20tailoring%20room%20tells%20a%20different%20story.%20The%20machines%20may%20be%20old.%20The%20walls%20may%20be%20bare.%20But%20the%20futures%20being%20stitched%20together%20here%20are%20full%20of%20colour%2C%20courage%2C%20and%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20garment%20made%20is%20more%20than%20fabric.%20It%20is%20proof%20that%20every%20woman%20who%20picks%20up%20a%20needle%20here%20is%20not%20just%20making%20clothes.%20She%E2%80%99s%20making%20her%20place%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752028200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-08T172815.759-1751976045.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D463107%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20stitching%20class.%20It%E2%80%99s%20where%20200%2B%20women%20are%20reclaiming%20self-worth%20through%20employment%2C%20skills%2C%20and%20basic%20education%20in%20a%20place%20built%20on%20sisterhood%20and%20compassion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F463107%2Fsahas-wishes-blessings-women-empowerment-delhi%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Days%20after%20Texas%20floods%