actory%20in%20New%20Bombay%20took%20over%20operations.%20%E2%80%9CIce%20first%20came%20to%20India%20on%20a%20ship%20from%20Boston%20in%20the%201800s%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20ice%2C%20history%20tells%20us%2C%20was%20stored%20in%20ice%20houses%20in%20Mumbai%20but%20India%E2%80%99s%20heat%20posed%20a%20challenge.%20So%2C%20businessmen%20Nanabhoy%20Byramjee%20Jeejeebhoy%20and%20JA%20Forbes%20launched%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20first%20ice%20factory%20in%20Ballard%20Estate%20in%201878.%20It%20was%20christened%20%E2%80%98Bombay%20Ice%20Manufacturing%20Co%E2%80%99%20before%20being%20rebranded%20as%20%E2%80%98Ambico%20Ice%20Factory%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%202019%2C%20when%20Malik%20first%20set%20sight%20on%20the%20building%2C%20he%20acquired%20it%20but%20with%20no%20plans%20to%20renovate%20or%20repurpose%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366166%2Fcossimbazar-palace-of-roys-rajbari-murshidabad-west-bengal-ancestral-palaces-heritage-hotel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epiece%20of%20history%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20banyan%20tree%2C%20however%2C%20would%20etch%20an%20image%20in%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20mind%20that%20would%20eventually%20become%20the%20seed%20that%20would%20reinvigorate%20the%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20had%20no%20idea%2C%20whatsoever%2C%20of%20either%20acquiring%20such%20a%20space%20or%20wanting%20to%20do%20something%20with%20it.%20But%20the%20image%20of%20the%20banyan%20tree%20stayed%20with%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20Malik%20found%20himself%20saying%20a%20%E2%80%98yes%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20project%2C%20joined%20by%20Abhijit%20Mehta%2C%20Arjun%20Malik%2C%20and%20Amrita%20Malik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20Malik%20Architecture%2C%20the%20team%20embarked%20on%20the%20quest%20to%20give%20the%20ice%20factory%20a%20second%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20IF.BE%20is%20a%2010%2C000-square-foot%20space%20that%20boasts%20five%20sections%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98The%20Banyan%20Tree%20Caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99%3B%20%E2%80%98The%20Substation%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F145074%2Flibrary-books-ruchi-dhona-children-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereading%20room%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20shop%20for%20architectural%20instruments%20and%20books%3B%20the%20%E2%80%98Ice%20Factory%E2%80%99%20designed%20for%20performances%3B%20%E2%80%98The%20Cathedral%E2%80%99%20where%20the%20bulk%20of%20exhibitions%20take%20place%3B%20and%20the%20fine%20dining%20Indian%20restaurant%2C%20Native%20Bombay%2C%20where%20guests%20fuel%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIF.BE%3A%20Stitching%20sustainability%20with%20history%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20of%20the%20project%20and%20the%20addition%20of%20the%20dot%20between%20the%20words%20do%20not%20skip%20my%20attention.%20Elaborating%20on%20it%2C%20Malik%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20dot%20%E2%80%94%20that%20gap%20between%20%E2%80%98if%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98be%E2%80%99%20symbolises%20time.%20If%20and%20be%20%E2%80%94%20the%20possibilities.%E2%80%9D%20And%20this%20is%20essentially%20the%20message%20that%20the%20architects%20have%20attempted%20to%20convey%2C%20the%20freedom%20that%20comes%20with%20the%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Malik%20details%20the%20restoration%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20evident%3A%20the%20rendering%20was%20rooted%20in%20honest%20appreciation%20of%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20history.%20The%20end%20goal%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20simply%20aesthetics%2C%20but%20to%20preserve%20the%20antiquity%20of%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-53-1751977084.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20major%20portion%20of%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20Ambico%20Ice%20Factory%20involved%20repurposing%20the%20Burma%20Teak%20that%20was%20found%20under%20the%20plaster%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-53-1751977084.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-53-1751977084-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-53-1751977084-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-53-1751977084-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-53-1751977084-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-465918%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cem%3EA%20major%20portion%20of%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20Ambico%20Ice%20Factory%20involved%20repurposing%20the%20Burma%20Teak%20that%20was%20found%20under%20the%20plaster%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2030%20months%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpainstaking%20efforts%E2%80%9D%20were%20directed%20towards%20retaining%20existing%20details%20that%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20legacy%2C%20in%20a%20more%20nuanced%20fashion.%20Malik%20adds%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332749%2Fex-banker-sunando-sen-built-tanhau-sustainable-himalayan-homestay-corbett-restore-wildlife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etouches%20of%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0were%20included%20in%20every%20way%20possible.%20For%20months%2C%20the%20team%20scraped%20away%20at%20old%20plaster%2C%20which%20yielded%20brickwork%20and%20vintage%20Burma%20teak%20woodwork%20underneath.%20Look%20around%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20notice%20in%20some%20places%20the%20colours%20don%E2%80%99t%20quite%20match.%20Malik%20underscores%20that%20no%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20polish%20the%20teak%20wood%20surfaces.%20This%20lends%20a%20rugged%2C%20raw%20touch%20to%20the%20staircase%20at%20the%20Native%20Restaurant%20and%20Bar%2C%20its%20roof%20structure%20and%20flooring%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Ice%20Factory%20roof%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20if%20there%20are%20mismatches%3F%20It%20only%20adds%20to%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20space%2C%20the%20architect%20believes.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20in%20places%20where%20it%20was%20necessitated%2C%20safety%20upgrades%20were%20made.%20These%20include%20structural%20reinforcements%20to%20the%20walls%20and%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20that%20took%20the%20most%20amount%20of%20brainstorming%2C%20Malik%20shares%2C%20was%20the%20main%20Ice%20Factory%2C%20sub-station%2C%20cold%20storage%2C%20and%20the%20ice-cubing%20area.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20required%20intensive%20examination%20and%20surgical%20intervention%20through%20retrofits%20to%20stabilise%20crumbling%2C%20warped%2C%20and%20leaking%20walls%2C%20sagging%20roofs%20and%20trusses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20every%20adventure%20story%2C%20the%20most%20exciting%20part%20is%20when%20a%20treasure%20is%20discovered.%20When%20the%20team%20stumbled%20upon%20giant%20cooling%20coils%20that%20were%20once%20used%20to%20manufacture%20ice%2C%20they%20were%20thrilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20have%20also%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F309116%2Fias-officer-anshul-gupta-efi-volunteers-restore-pond-wildlife-ujjain-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeatured%20in%20the%20restoration%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20are%20embedded%20in%20the%20glass%20floor%20towards%20the%20entrance.%20Another%20treasure%20lay