in%20they%20had%20more%20efficiently.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-07T191851.197-1751896396.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-07T191851.197-1751896396-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-07T191851.197-1751896396-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-07T191851.197-1751896396-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-07T191851.197-1751896396-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-465350%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELocal%20communities%20realised%20that%20instead%20of%20chasing%20water%2C%20they%20needed%20to%20trap%20and%20use%20what%20little%20rain%20they%20had%20more%20efficiently.%20Picture%20source%3A%20DynamiteNews%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F138953%2Fkiwi-farmers-arunachal-ziro%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20Ziro%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Apatani%20system%20continues%20to%20be%20part%20of%20everyday%20life%2C%20sustained%20by%20tribal%20customs%20and%20village%20councils.%20Water%20distribution%2C%20field%20maintenance%2C%20and%20fish%20stocking%20are%20often%20communal%20tasks.%20While%20some%20modern%20inputs%20have%20crept%20in%2C%20many%20households%20still%20rely%20primarily%20on%20organic%20waste%2C%20traditional%20seed%20varieties%2C%20and%20local%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20stands%20out%20in%20both%20cases%20is%20that%20these%20systems%20are%20self-regulating%2C%20low-cost%2C%20and%20rely%20heavily%20on%20community%20participation%E2%80