20every%20city%20has%20two%20or%20three%20chocolate%20brands%20like%20his%20mithai%20brands%2C%20but%20if%20they%20all%20source%20the%20same%20ingredients%20from%20the%20same%20multinational%20supplier%2C%20the%20end%20product%20will%20be%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELiving%20with%20Farmers%2C%20Learning%20from%20the%20Soil%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20researching%20the%20art%20of%20chocolate%20making%2C%20small-batch%20chocolate%20production%2C%20and%20the%20principles%20of%20craft%20chocolate%2C%20his%20study%20found%20a%20key%20understanding%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20chocolate%20inherently%20depends%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20beans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20prompted%20him%20to%20search%20further%20about%20the%20origin%20of%20beans%2C%20and%20that%20led%20him%20to%20farms%20in%202018%2C%20where%20he%20spent%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20with%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20West%20Godavari%20district%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20the%20farmers%20were%20skeptical.%20They%20viewed%20me%20as%20an%20outsider%20from%20the%20city%20doing%20something%20new.%20I%20lived%20among%20them%20to%20win%20their%20trust.%20It%20took%20two%20to%20three%20years%20to%20build%20their%20confidence%20in%20me.%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20business%20with%20them%20and%20help%20them%20make%20more%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20businessperson%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms-of-Member-Farmers_West-Godavari_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_2550e_11zon-1751876747-500x750.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms-of-Member-Farmers_West-Godavari_Ph