%20and%20DOPL%2C%20we%20are%20not%20treated%20like%20suppliers%20but%20as%20partners%2C%20even%20co-creators.%20Earlier%2C%20we%20used%20to%20grow%20cocoa%20without%20really%20knowing%20how%20much%20impact%20the%20soil%2C%20the%20climate%2C%20or%20our%20handling%20could%20have%20on%20the%20flavour%20of%20the%20cocoa%20beans.%20The%20engagement%20has%20enhanced%20our%20understanding%20that%20cocoa%20carries%20the%20taste%20of%20the%20land%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20our%20job%20to%20bring%20that%20out%20with%20our%20efforts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20different%20about%20working%20with%20them%20is%20the%20respect%20they%20have%20for%20our%20offering.%20They%20pay%20us%20above-market%20rates%20for%20our%20fruit%2C%20but%20more%20than%20that%2C%20we%20see%20the%20value%20of%20what%20we%20grow.%20When%20our%20cacao%20goes%20through%20their%20Fermentery%20with%20all%20the%20scientific%20fermentation%20and%20drying%20processes%20that%20they%20carry%20out%20and%20it%20is%20turned%20into%20fine%20flavour%20cacao%20beans%2C%20it%20gives%20us%20tremendous%20pride.%20We%20know%20exactly%20where%20our%20fruit%20is%20going%2C%20and%20we%20know%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20made%20into%20something%20truly%20special.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20farmers%20here%20produced%20cocoa%20in%20a%20conventional%20method%2C%20Muppala%20faced%20another%20challenge%20related%20to%20the%20genetics%20of%20cocoa%20in%20India%2C%20which%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20the%20history%20of%20its%20arrival%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-500x739.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-500x739.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-203x300.jpg%20203w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-768x1135.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-1039x1536.jpg%201039w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-1386x2048.jpg%201386w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-150x222.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-465025%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22739%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20Manam%20Chocolate%20Karkhana%2C%20processing%2C%20retailing%2C%20and%20crafting%20of%20chocolate%20are%20combined%20under%20a%20single%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20addressed%20the%20genetic%20problem%20through%20technological%20solutions%20developed%20by%20our%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Muppala%2C%20who%20noted%20that%20India%20grows%20only%200.5%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20cocoa.%20Even%20if%20the%20production%20were%20to%20increase%20fourfold%2C%20the%20output%20would%20only%20represent%202%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20cocoa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20small%20area%20of%20land%20creates%20barriers%20to%20being%20a%20major%20player.%20The%20crop%20demands%20specific%20environmental%20conditions%2C%20including%20sufficient%20water%20and%20shade.%20It%20grows%20only%20between%2020%C2%B0%20north%20and%2020%C2%B0%20south%20of%20the%20Equator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20may%20never%20be%20a%20major%20cocoa-growing%20country%2C%20but%20we%20can%20make%20India%20a%20%E2%80%98premium%E2%80%99%20cocoa-growing%20nation.%20After%20having%20engaged%20over%20150%20farmers%20cultivating%20cocoa%20across%20a%20collective%20area%20of%203%2C000%20acres%20and%20making%20it%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20cocoa-growing%20region%2C%20we%20constructed%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20largest%20fine-flavour%20cocoa%20fermentary%20at%20Tadikalapudi%20in%20West%20Godavari%20on%20a%20four-acre%20land%20in%202021%2C%20where%20we%20execute%20fermentation%20and%20drying%20with%20our%20advanced%20scientific%20technique%2C%E2%80%9D%20Muppala%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20story%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehalwai%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20wanted%20to%20craft%20chocolate%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20270%20people%20worked%20on%20this%20project%20over%20four%20years%2C%20culminating%20in%20its%20launch.%20Muppala%20realized%20he%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehalwai%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20wanted%20to%20craft%20chocolate%20but%20ended%20up%20making%20something%20else.%20What%20about%20chocolate%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20came%20back%20to%20Hyderabad%20and%20started%20structuring%20what%20chocolate%20can%20be%20and%20should%20be%20for%20India%20as%20well%20as%20from%20India%20for%20the%20world.%20It%E2%80%99s%20our%20social%20proclivity%20as%20Indians%20to%20gift%2C%20share%2C%20and%20consume%20sweets%2C%E2%80%9D%20mentions%20Muppala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuppala%20has%20invested%20significantly%20in%20the%20business%2C%20including%20creating%20the%20Manam%20Chocolate%20Karkhana%2C%20where%20the%20processing%2C%20retailing%2C%20and%20crafting%20of%20chocolate%20are%20combined%20under%20a%20single%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpanning%20an%20area%20of%2010%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20the%20Karkhana%20offers%20a%20chance%20to%20discover%2C%20explore%2C%20experience%2C%20and%20engage%20with%20cacao%20and%20chocolate%20in%20a%20dynamic%20and%20interactive%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739-1536x1536.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739-96x96.jpg%2096w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739.jpg%201624w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-465026%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhatever%20tablet%20or%20bar%20one%20buys%2C%20there%20is%20a%20QR%20code%20on%20the%20back.%20When%20scanned%2C%20it%20provides%20information%20about%20the%20farm%2C%20the%20farmer%2C%20and%20the%20harvest%20date.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20a%20visitor%20or%20a%20customer%2C%20one%20can%20experience%20the%20captivating%20transformation%20of%20raw%20cacao%20beans%20into%20silky%2C%20delectable%20chocolate%20as%20it%20passes%20through%20roasting%2C%20winnowing%2C%20grinding%2C%20refining%2C%20conching%2C%20tempering%2C%20and%20moulding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20tablet%20or%20bar%20one%20buys%2C%20there%20is%20a%20QR%20code%20on%20the%20back.%20When%20scanned%2C%20it%20provides%20information%20about%20the%20farm%2C%20the%20farmer%2C%20and%20the%20harvest%20date.%20All%20this%20data%20is%20sourced%20from%20the%20blockchain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20developed%20our%20technology.%20It%20highlights%20the%20traceability%20of%20cocoa%20through%20a%20blockchain-enabled%20system.%20Every%20single%20bean%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20its%20exact%20farm.%20However%2C%20the%20supermarket%20chocolate%20provides%20no%20information%20about%20the%20source%20of%20the%20cocoa%20bean%2C%E2%80%9D%20Muppala%20quipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarkhana%20is%20now%20reaping%20the%20rewards.%20In%20its%20first%20year%2C%20the%20company%2C%20which%20employs%20around%20200%20people%2C%20recorded%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs.%208.79%20crore%2C%20achieved%20in%20only%20eight%20months%20of%20operation%20during%20the%20fiscal%20year%202023-24.%20The%20chocolate%20maker%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20growing%20150%25%20year-on-year.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20successful%20market%20strategy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20imports%20more%20than%2070%25%20of%20its%20cocoa%20needs%20despite%20having%20grown%20cocoa%20for%20over%20six%20decades.%20Muppala%20recently%20started%20exporting%20beans%20to%20the%20world.%20This%20February%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20a%20major%20consignment%20of%20fine%20flavoured%20cocoa%20has%20been%20exported%20from%20India%20to%20Switzerland%2C%20where%20a%20major%20Swiss%20chocolate%20brand%20is%20making%20a%20single-origin%20India%20chocolate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20farmers%2C%20fermenters%2C%20chocolate%20makers%2C%20chocolatiers%2C%20and%20storytellers.%20We%20see%20ourselves%20as%20craftspeople.%20Starting%20with%20the%20farmers%2C%20who%20craft%20at%20the%20source%2C%20then%20a%20fermenter%2C%20then%20a%20chocolate%20maker.%20Our%20story%20starts%20on%20the%20farms.%20Every%20store%20we%20open%2C%20our%20farmer%20has%20to%20open%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20concludes%20the%20chocolate%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20it%20take%20to%20create%20fine-flavour%20cocoa%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20agro-climatic%20conditions%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoyapati%20Venkateswara%20Rao%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20member%20farmers%20associated%20with%20Distinct%20Origins%2C%20who%20owns%20one%20of%20the%20first%20organic%20cocoa%20farm%20in%20West%20Godavari%20District%20in%20AP%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20early%20days%2C%20we%20relied%20heavily%20on%20chemical%20sprays%20and%20fertilizers%20to%20keep%20the%20cacao%20plants%20healthy.%20But%20over%20the%20past%20five%20to%20six%20years%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20started%20returning%20to%20more%20natural%2C%20sustainable%20practices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%20further%20mentions%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20found%20that%20using%20vermicompost%20significantly%20improves%20soil%20health%2C%20strengthens%20the%20trees%2C%20and%20keeps%20the%20roots%20active.%20We%20also%20apply%20coconut%20husk%20mulch%20around%20the%20base%20of%20each%20plant%20%E2%80%94%20it%20helps%20retain%20soil%20moisture%20and%20keeps%20the%20roots%20cool%20during%20hot%20weather.%20The%20result%20is%20better%20fruit%20size%2C%20more%20consistent%20pod%20quality%2C%20and%20overall%20healthier%20trees.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F6_Dried-Cacao-Beans_-Distint-Origins-Cacao-Fermentery_West-Godavari-DistrictAP_-photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_4473-copy_11zon-1751876725-500x342.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%